- Remove duplicate ApiKeyModal from UserMenu dropdown
- Remove API key inputs from PrivacySettings (now Language tab)
- Rename Privacy tab to Language with globe icon
- Add defaultTab prop to SettingsModal for direct navigation
- Consolidate API key management to ApiKeysSection only

Users now configure API keys in one place: Settings > API Keys tab.
